data.description: Experience the epitome of comfortable elegance in this exquisite nearly new construction home situated on a sprawling 1.45-acre lot within the esteemed Whitewater Schools district. This upgraded Jeff Lindsey Greywell B Floor plan residence has been meticulously maintained and enhanced by its current owner in a short span.    Extended driveway offers convenience, complete with a bump-out area for easy vehicle maneuvering. Step inside to discover a truly spectacular interior, adorned with custom lighting fixtures that enhance its charm. Gorgeous Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring graces the main level, while plush carpeting provides comfort in the bedrooms and office space.    Upon entering through the upgraded double doors, you'll find a welcoming foyer with a coffered ceiling. To the left, an oversized dining room boasts wainscoting on the walls, easily accommodating a large dining table. Let the natural light flood the open and airy floor plan living space overlooking the serene backyard. The great room takes center stage with its floor-to-ceiling stacked stone fireplace.    The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring 2 large double islands & coffee bar, with Quartz countertops, a JL Signature Cabinet-style walk-in pantry, and a stainless farmhouse sink. All stainless Frigidaire appliances, including a double oven, gas bump-out cooktop, and dishwasher.  Complete with dining space for informal dinners and additional sitting area space, this open concept kitchen/great room combo is perfect for large gatherings.    The primary bedroom and ensuite on the main level exude luxury, with a spa-style large shower, soaking tub, an expansive vanity, and an expansive and opulent closet offering lavish space for all your storage needs.      Another en-suite on the main level is perfect for a second office or an in-law bedroom. Finishing off the main level include laundry room generously sized and offering a window view, complete with ample cabinetry for storage and a cabinet-style sink with a granite top. Nearby, a 3-station mud bench is conveniently located near the garage entrance.    Upstairs, you'll find three additional bedrooms, one of which is a full en-suite with private bathroom and closet, doubling as an entertainment room if desired.  Huge unfinished storage area accessible from jack-and-jill bathroom between secondary upstairs bedrooms.    Indulge in outdoor gatherings while savoring barbecues on the expansive covered patio, seamlessly connected to an additional pathway leading to the detached garage. Abundant storage options await for your vehicles, boats, and miscellaneous belongings within the attached 3-car garage or the 676 sq ft detached 2-car garage, complete with a well-appointed upper level for supplementary storage or create your own personal space as heating and cooling already installed.    The vast and open backyard creates a captivating scene, evoking the tranquility of a countryside vista. This remarkable residence enjoys an optimal location, mere minutes from shopping amenities, with easy accessibility to Trilith, Peachtree City, Fayetteville, and Senoia.
